</pre>

<pre style="font-size:150%; float:left; width: 33%";>
_#_o_01 GOOD...
_#_o_02   ▆ any change to a source repo triggers 
_#_o_03     an event
_#_o_04   ▆ rebuild of repo container
_#_o_05   ▆ test of new container in whole system
_#_o_06   ▆ attempt at testing isolated effect of
_#_o_07     new module or system
