<pre style="font-size:150%; float:left; width: 33%">
_#_o_08 BAD...
_#_o_09   ▆ TravisCI only covers dev environment
_#_o_10   ▆ dev uses docker swarm, 
_#_o_11     deploy uses openshift
_#_o_12   ▆ unable to properly test deployment
_#_o_13     compute topology
</pre>

<pre style="font-size:150%; float:right; width: 33%">
_#_o_14 UGLY...
